{
  "id": "adv_event_2203_01_05",
  "title": "私達のやり方で",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――練習開始から数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days after the start of the practice",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 1.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、おはよう、起きてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ good morning‚ are you awake?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4666666667,
      "endTime": 5.5968480269,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、瑠依さん\nお、おはよう、ございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rui-san.\nG-Good morning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8,
      "endTime": 10.1691373162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 10.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "朝食、一緒に食べない？\nレッスンの前に、話をしたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Want to have breakfast together?\nI want to talk before the lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3666666667,
      "endTime": 15.4550793711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 15.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……今は、その、ちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ um‚ I'm a bit busy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6333333333,
      "endTime": 19.249682601299998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしても、やらないといけないことがあって……\nごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's something I really have to do…\nI'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "endTime": 24.9459264694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 25.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1333333333,
      "endTime": 26.6666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "…………ふぅ、ごちそうさま",
      "translations": {
        "en": "sigh…Nice meal…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9,
      "endTime": 31.666575861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　もう食べないの？\n随分、残してるけど、めずらしいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? You're not eating anymore?\nYou're leaving quite a bit‚ that's unusual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8666666667,
      "endTime": 39.1035536702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、もしかして……私の味付け、口に合わなかった？\nえへへ、まだお料理は勉強中で……ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ could it be… my seasoning didn't suit your taste?\nHehe‚ I'm still learning how to cook… Sorry about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3,
      "endTime": 50.3273078733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、そうじゃないの\n渚の料理は美味しかったけど、食欲がなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no‚ that's not it.\nNagisa's cooking was delicious‚ but I just don't have an appetite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5333333333,
      "endTime": 56.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、雫ちゃんとのレッスン\nうまくいってないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be because of the\nlessons with Shizuku-chan? Not going well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1666666667,
      "endTime": 62.91,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "あれから毎日、二人で沢山\n練習してるみたいだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been practicing together\nevery day since then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0666666667,
      "endTime": 67.6766402562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "形にはなってきたと思う。でも、雫の声が……\nあの時聴いた、素敵な歌声が出てないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's starting to take shape‚ but Shizuku's voice…\nThat beautiful singing voice I heard that time isn't coming out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9333333333,
      "endTime": 78.4507693168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "私が参加したのは、雫の歌声を活かしたいから\n……でも、このままじゃ意味がない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I joined because I wanted to make use of Shizuku's singing voice.\n…But it's meaningless like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7333333333,
      "endTime": 86.7398396122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "……どうして、そうなっちゃったのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wonder why it turned out this way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87,
      "endTime": 89.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "…………原因が思いつかないの\n私、今まで優とすみれとしかやったことがないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I can't think of the cause.\nI've only done it with Yu and Sumire before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.0666666667,
      "endTime": 97.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "こういう時、どうすればいいのか分からない\n雫……落ち込んでいるし、こんなの初めて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know what to do in these situations.\nShizuku… she's feeling down‚ this is the first time for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1333333333,
      "endTime": 107.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "サニピで出来ていることが、私と一緒だと出来ない\nつまり……私に原因があるのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing she usual does in Sunny Peace isn't working with me.\nIn other words… it's my fault.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1333333333,
      "endTime": 116.55257814020001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとちょっと！\n瑠依ちゃんまで落ち込んじゃダメだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute!\nRui-chan‚ you can't be down too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9,
      "endTime": 120.5044898669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "私は、雫のパフォーマンスを引き出したい\n渚、雫ってどんな子なの？　お願い、教えて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to bring out Shizuku's performance.\nNagisa‚ what kind of person is Shizuku? Please tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7,
      "endTime": 130.7923077902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "……うーん、そうだね\n雫ちゃんは口下手で、普段の口数は少なくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ let's see…\nShizuku-chan is not good with words and usually doesn't say much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1,
      "endTime": 140.2766864101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、時々凄く鋭いことを言うんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But sometimes‚ she says really sharp things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5,
      "endTime": 144.8616555214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "……どういう意味？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1666666667,
      "endTime": 146.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "物事の核心をつくの。みんなハッとなるくらい\nそれで、違和感とかに気付くんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She gets to the core of things that make everyone surpirse.\nSo she notices things that don't feel right or something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.2666666667,
      "endTime": 155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "……違和感に、気付く……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't feel right or something….?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2,
      "endTime": 157.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "この間、サニピのみんなで作詞をした時\nどうしても、しっくりこなかったみたいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we were all working on lyrics in Sunny Peace recently‚\nthere was something that didn't fit no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7333333333,
      "endTime": 164.0307692307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_05-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな時、雫ちゃんのアドバイスがヒントになって\n解決したことがあったんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And at that time‚ Shizuku-chan's advice became a clue\nand helped us solve it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.2333333333,
      "endTime": 170,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
